Class Cache

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--net.sourceforge.gjtapi.util.Cache
Direct Known Subclasses:
SoftMap, WeakMap
public abstract class Cache
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Map

This is an abstract cache Map of keys to values where the values are held in References which will allow them to be collected by a garbage collector when memory gets low.

Concreate subclasses define which type of references are used. Creation date: (2000-06-08 12:16:14)
